elegatesJdbcOperationsToPhysicalConnection() throws Exception {\n        RecordingDataSource nestedDataSource = new RecordingDataSource();\n        WrapperConnectionPoolDataSource poolDataSource = new WrapperConnectionPoolDataSource(false);\n        poolDataSource.setNestedDataSource(nestedDataSource);\n        poolDataSource.setUsesTraditionalReflectiveProxies(true);\n\n        PooledConnection pooledConnection = poolDataSource.getPooledConnection();\n        try {\n            Connection connection = pooledConnection.getConnection();\n\n            assertThat(connection.toString()).contains(\"C3P0ProxyConnection\");\n            assertThat(connection.getAutoCommit()).isTrue();\n\n            connection.setTransactionIsolation(Connection.TRANSACTION_READ_COMMITTED);\n            connection.setCatalog(DEFAULT_CATALOG);\n            connection.setHoldability(ResultSet.CLOSE_CURSORS_AT_COMMIT);\n\n            try (Statement statement = connection.createStatement();\n                    PreparedStatement preparedStatement = connection.prepareStatement(\"select 1\");\n                    CallableStatement callableStatement = connection.prepareCall(\"call test()\")) {\n                assertThat(statement).isNotNull();\n                assertThat(preparedStatement).isNotNull();\n                assertThat(callableStatement).isNotNull();\n            }\n\n            C3P0ProxyConnection proxyConnection = (C3P0ProxyConnection) connection;\n            Method createStatement = Connection.class.getMethod(\"createStatement\");\n            try (Statement rawStatement = (Statement) proxyConnection.rawConnectionOperation(\n                    createStatement, C3P0ProxyConnection.RAW_CONNECTION, new Object[0])) {\n                assertThat(rawStatement).isNotNull();\n            }\n\n            connection.close();\n\n            assertThat(nestedDataSource.connectionHandler.calls)\n                    .containsKeys(\n                            \"getAutoCommit\",\n                            \"setTransactionIsolation\",\n                            \"setCatalog\",\n                            \"setHoldability\",\n                            \"createStatement\",\n                            \"prepareStatement\",\n                            \"prepareCall\");\n        } finally {\n            pooledConnection.close();\n        }\n    }\n\n    public static class RecordingDataSource implements DataSource {\n        private final RecordingJdbcHandler connectionHandler = new RecordingJdbcHandler(Connection.class);\n\n        @Override\n        public Connection getConnection() {\n            return connectionHandler.createProxy(Connection.class);\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public Connection getConnection(String username, String password) {\n            return getConnection();\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public PrintWriter getLogWriter() throws SQLException {\n            return null;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public void setLogWriter(PrintWriter out) throws SQLException {\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public void setLoginTimeout(int seconds) throws SQLException {\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public int getLoginTimeout() throws SQLException {\n            return 0;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public Logger getParentLogger() throws SQLFeatureNotSupportedException {\n            throw new SQLFeatureNotSupportedException();\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public <T> T unwrap(Class<T> iface) throws SQLException {\n            if (iface.isInstance(this)) {\n                return iface.cast(this);\n            }\n            throw new SQLException(\"Not a wrapper for \" + iface.getName());\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public boolean isWrapperFor(Class<?> iface) {\n            return iface.isInstance(this);\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static final class RecordingJdbcHandler implements InvocationHandler {\n        private final Class<?> jdbcInterface;\n        private final Map<String, Integer> calls;\n        private boolean autoCommit = true;\n        private boolean closed;\n        private int holdability = ResultSet.CLOSE_CURSORS_AT_COMMIT;\n        private int transactionIsolation = Connection.TRANSACTION_READ_COMMITTED;\n        private String catalog = DEFAULT_CATALOG;\n\n        private RecordingJdbcHandler(Class<?> jdbcInterface) {\n            this(jdbcInterface, new HashMap<>());\n        }\n\n        private RecordingJdbcHandler(Class<?> jdbcInterface, Map<String, Integer> calls) {\n            this.jdbcInterface = jdbcInterface;\n            this.calls = calls;\n        }\n\n        private <T> T createProxy(Class<T> proxyInterface) {\n            Object proxy = Proxy.newProxyInstance(\n                    C3P0PooledConnectionInnerProxyConnectionInvocationHandlerTest.class.getClassLoader(),\n                    new Class<?>[] {proxyInterface},\n                    this);\n            return proxyInterface.cast(proxy);\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public Object invoke(Object proxy, Method method, Object[] args) throws Throwable {\n            String methodName = method.getName();\n            if (method.getDeclaringClass() == Object.class) {\n                return handleObjectMethod(proxy, methodName, args);\n            }\n\n            calls.merge(methodName, 1, Integer::sum);\n            if (jdbcInterface == Connection.class) {\n                return handleConnectionMethod(method, args);\n            }\n            if (\"close\".equals(methodName)) {\n                closed = true;\n                return null;\n            }\n            if (\"isClosed\".equals(methodName)) {\n                return closed;\n            }\n            return defaultValue(method.getReturnType());\n        }\n\n        private Object handleObjectMethod(Object proxy, String methodName, Object[] args) {\n            if (\"toString\".equals(methodName)) {\n                return \"Recording \" + jdbcInterface.getSimpleName();\n            }\n            if (\"hashCode\".equals(methodName)) {\n                return System.identityHashCode(proxy);\n            }\n            if (\"equals\".equals(methodName)) {\n                return proxy == args[0];\n            }\n            throw new UnsupportedOperationException(methodName);\n        }\n\n        private Object handleConnectionMethod(Method method, Object[] args) {\n            String methodName = method.getName();\n            if (\"getAutoCommit\".equals(methodName)) {\n                return autoCommit;\n            }\n            if (\"setAutoCommit\".equals(methodName)) {\n                autoCommit = (Boolean) args[0];\n                return null;\n            }\n            if (\"getTransactionIsolation\".equals(methodName)) {\n                return transactionIsolation;\n            }\n            if (\"setTransactionIsolation\".equals(methodName)) {\n                transactionIsolation = (Integer) args[0];\n                return null;\n            }\n            if (\"getCatalog\".equals(methodName)) {\n                return catalog;\n            }\n            if (\"setCatalog\".equals(methodName)) {\n                catalog = (String) args[0];\n                return null;\n            }\n            if (\"getHoldability\".equals(methodName)) {\n                return holdability;\n            }\n            if (\"setHoldability\".equals(methodName)) {\n                holdability = (Integer) args[0];\n                return null;\n            }\n            if (\"createStatement\".equals(methodName)) {\n                return new RecordingJdbcHandler(Statement.class, calls).createProxy(Statement.class);\n            }\n            if (\"prepareStatement\".equals(methodName)) {\n                return new RecordingJdbcHandler(PreparedStatement.class, calls).createProxy(PreparedStatement.class);\n            }\n            if (\"prepareCall\".equals(methodName)) {\n                return new RecordingJdbcHandler(CallableStatement.class, calls).createProxy(CallableStatement.class);\n            }\n            if (\"getTypeMap\".equals(methodName)) {\n                return new HashMap<String, Class<?>>();\n            }\n            if (\"close\".equals(methodName)) {\n                closed = true;\n                return null;\n            }\n            if (\"isClosed\".equals(methodName)) {\n                return closed;\n            }\n            if (\"isValid\".equals(methodName)) {\n                return !closed;\n            }\n            return defaultValue(method.getReturnType());\n        }\n\n        private Object defaultValue(Class<?> returnType) {\n            if (returnType == Void.TYPE) {\n                return null;\n            }\n            if (!returnType.isPrimitive()) {\n                return null;\n            }\n            if (returnType == Boolean.TYPE) {\n                return false;\n            }\n            if (returnType == Character.TYPE) {\n                return '\\0';\n            }\n\n[23 more lines in file. Use offset=261 to continue.]"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1780845442704}]}
